<font color="#FF0000">RESPONSE TO ARTHUR V.</font><br>
<tt>Sat May 31  0:28:11 US/Eastern 1997
</tt><p>
Arthur, I want no fight with you, nor do I wish a stay in your head. Please rethink and reconsider.  I know you worked to get where you are, and I respect that labor.  It is the likes of Nurse Ratchet that sucks you off, just as now, when you flame at me, because of his work.  Feelings, of yes, I have them, 100's in fact. But I do not want to see any &quot;friends&quot; and yes, I consider you as one, ripped off by a sleaze merchant, and that is what I see the good Nurse as. Check it out with DocDel or Chet, or Wingman, et al. We had this fight with the troller named Ratchet, and we don't need to fight it again.<br><br>
Money may rule the world, but for you and me, it is the morgage payment, the car payment, and busting out butts each and every month to get by.  Don't get tricked by the intellectual and glib bullshit spit on you by Nurse R. He is the worse cynic there is.  He is the lifer who will pull you down into his hellhole, not inspire nor lift you up into creative thinking.  Look back in the archives, this is a done thing. And I was not alone.<br><br>
I am no more an expert on most of these matters than you are, and probably less.  I don't even think I am expert on Psych stuff, cause it changes so much, after 25 years of doing it.  But, and this is crucial, you got to (1) keep an open mind at all times, and (2) know when you are being hussled.  Believe me, and many others, the Nurse ain't on line to help you, but to further his own sick trip.  I will let others prove me right or wrong.<br><br>
doc spatz
